\id PHM - Borna New Testamnet
\h Filimon
\toc2 Filimon
\toc1 Filimon Maants
\toc3 Film.
\mt3 Wosheetso P'awlos Wosho
\mt1 Filimon Maants
\imt1 Kindo
\ip Filimon daneek krstiyaniya b́tesh, K'olasiyas Ik'i mootsi ashe b́teshok'o danofaletuwe. Filimon Onismosi eteets guutso detsfe b́tesh, guutsanúwere b́doonzoke t'aft bíamtsok'oon tipimootse teshtso P'awlosnton b́gonkeyi, P'awlos weeron Onismos krstiyani wotat bíamani, P'awlos Filimon maants b́ guut'ts wosho filimon b́maants aanar woke fa'a guutsonton b́maneetuwok'o gawitka b́tesh, manats dabtuwere and Onisimos krstiyani b́wottsotse haniyere hakon krstiyani eshuwok'o bín b́dek'etuwok'owa bako guutsok'o b́taawurawok'owe bísh b́keewiri.
\iot Jamon mas'aafan b́detstso
\io1 Kindo 1-3
\io1 P'awlos udo Filimonsh 4-7
\io1 P'awlos Onosimos jango b́ t'intsts kup'ts k'ono 8-22
\io1 Gúúpo 23-25
\c 1
\s1 Jamo
\p 
\v 1 Krstos Iyesus jangosh tipetso tiyoke P'awlosnat no eshu T'imotiyosokere, shunetso no eshuu no fini tooh wottsosh Filimonsh,
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt K'ol. 4:17\x* no mish Afbyash noonton Krstossh kaarts wottsosh Arikip'assh, mank'owere n meyits ko'eyiru amantsuwotssh,
\v 3 No nihi Ik'oke, no doonz Iyesus Krstos s'aatetonat jeenon itsh wotowe.
\s1 Filimon shunonat imnetiyon
\p 
\v 4 Ik'o tk'onor itn gawfetsat jam aawo Izar Izeweri udirwe,
\v 5 Doonzo Iyesussh n detsts shunonat imnetiyon ando amantsuwotssh shuno n detstsok'o shishre,
\v 6 Krstosk no wottsosh no detsts sheeng keew jamo keer b́ danetwok'o n imnetiyo k'oshwotssh kayiyosh n kúp'itwok'o Ik'o k'onitwe.
\v 7 Ti eshuwo! niatse tuutson amantsuwots nibo b́ handrtsosh n shuno een wotts gene'onat kúp'o taash imre.
\s1 P'awlos Onesimos jangosh Filimoni b́k'ontsok'o
\p 
\v 8 K'alo neesh b́geyitwo k'alwe err neen azazosh Krstosn ááw shuuk'o tdetsalor,
\v 9 mank'o k'aloniyere Krstos Iyesus jangosh tipetso taa eenasho P'awlos shunon k'ono marat'itwe.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt K'ol. 4:9\x* taa tipi mootse t beyor Shayiron t naayi wottso Onesimos jangosh neen k'onre.
\v 11 Onasimos haniyere shin k'awntsalke b́ teshi, andomo taash wotowa neeshor t'ak'amitke.
\p 
\v 12 Hambe bín niyok aanidek' woshere, bín niyok twoshoor t took níbo twoshtsok'o woshde'er taawitwe.
\v 13 Doo shishi jangosh hanokere tipeyat t beyor n shegro wotar taash b́ finish bí taanton b́wotink'e geneúyank'ee b́ teshi,
\v 14 Ernmó n sheeng fino angnon b́ woterawo shunon b́ wotituwok'owa etaat nee niekeraniyere eegoru k'alo geeratse.
\p 
\v 15 Onesimos andish b́ borfetso múk' gizewosh niyatse b́k'ale daneraka haniyere hakon jam gizeyosh neenton beyosh wotituwe.
\v 16 Haniyak guutsok'o b́ woterawo guutsoniyere bog wotar shuneets eshúwok'owiye, bí taash shuneets eeshúwe, neeshmó iki bogo aaw aawi b́ beyonat doonzon shune eshwok'oyiye.
\p 
\v 17 Eshe taanton tohaat finef tohok'o woshdek'at tawurne wotiyal arikon taank'o woshde'er bín de'e.
\v 18 Neen b́ dadtso fa'e wotiyal wee k'awntso biyatse fa'e wotiyal b́ k'awntsman tiyats woshuwe.
\v 19 Eshe taa P'awlos «Bíyatse fa'a k'awntso dashetwe» etaat t took kishon t guut'tsok'o danire, ernmó n kashosh nee n tookon dab taash k'awnts n wottsok'o taa neesh t gawiyo geyiratse.
\v 20 Eshe tí eshwo! sheeng keewan taash n k'alitwok'o doozon neen k'onirwe oona neesha t nibo Krstosn taash handriwe.
\p 
\v 21 Neesh t guut'tsansh taash ni'alletwok'o amanere, monk'owere taa ti aattsoniyere bogo n k'alituwok'o danfee.
\v 22 Mannowere Ik'o it k'ono shiyir itok t weetwok'o b́ woshitwok'o t tewnirwotse bíts t kashit moo taash k'aniwe.
\s1 S'uwaatsi jamo
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt K'ol. 1:7; 4:12\x* Krstos Iyesus jangosh taanton tipetso Ep'afra jamo itsh t'intsirwe,
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Wosh. 12:12, 25; 13:13; 15:37-39; 19:29; 27:2; K'ol. 4:10, 14; 2 T'im. 4:10-11\x* Mank'owere t fini tooh wottswots Mark'os, Arst'rokos, Demas, Luk'aswere jamo neesh t'intsirune.
\p 
\v 25 Doonzo Iyesus Krstos s'aato it Shayironton wotowe.
